name: MoonScape
description: MoonScape is a memecoin made for fun. There was no pvp game on Solana so we bring the first. A PVP game on that 2 players enter the Arena, only 1 leaves alive. You take double reward as the winner or nothing as loser. $MOON token will be used for rewarding the winner. 2 players put their $MOON token to win double. This means if you play well, you can double your $MOON token. We aim to be Solana's premier PvP game.
